Question: I am new to statistics. I found a script which makes a autocorrelogram graph(see attached) of spike timings of a neuron. I got the graph but I am not able to interpret it. Matlab Code below.

```
    function autocorrelogram(spiketimes)
    %spiketimes = [10413177585,10413282812,10413379677,10413402313,10413410739,10413422026,..]
        isi=[];
        for i = 1:length(spiketimes)
            isi = [isi; spiketimes-spiketimes(i)];
        end
        isi(isi>2000000)=[];
        isi(isi<-2000000)=[];
        isi=isi./1000000;
        save isi;
        figure
        hist(isi,-2:0.02:2);

```

